Putin Says Russian Government May Have Balanced Budget Next Year

-- B y   S c o t t   R o s e
-- 
2011-10-06T10:57:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-06/putin-says-russian-government-may-have-balanced-budget-next-year.html
Russian Prime Minister  Vladimir Putin 
said the government may balance its budget next year or run a
small deficit, depending on conditions in the world economy.  To contact the reporter on this story:
